title: JFK Assassination - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 11/22/21
itunes:title: JFK Assassination - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 11/22/21
description:
George Noory and author Dawna Kaufmann mark the 58th anniversary of the killing of President John F. Kennedy on November 22, 1963, discuss her investigation with forensic pathologist Dr. Cyril Wecht who does not believe the official account that Kennedy was killed by a single gunman, as well as the inconsistencies in the story of the killing of Robert F. Kennedy by Sirhan Sirhan.
